Excitement is brewing among fans as the release date for "Maxxxine," the third entry in the Mia Goth X trilogy, draws near. Directed by acclaimed filmmaker Ti West.

The star-studded cast assembled for "Maxxxine" is nothing short of impressive, featuring a lineup of talented actors and actresses. Leading the ensemble is Mia Goth, reprising her role as the enigmatic protagonist, alongside Elizabeth Debicki, Moses Sumney, Bobby Cannavale, Halsey, Michelle Monaghan, Giancarlo Esposito, Lily Collins, and Kevin Bacon.

"Maxxxine" is set to hit theaters on July 5, 2024, marking the culmination of the Mia Goth X trilogy. As anticipation continues to build, fans eagerly await the opportunity to immerse themselves in the thrilling world crafted by Ti West and brought to life by an exceptional cast.

Prepare to be swept away on a mesmerizing journey filled with intrigue, suspense, and unforgettable moments as "Maxxxine" arrives in theaters this summer. Don't miss your chance to witness the epic conclusion to one of cinema's most captivating trilogies.  
  
